cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.CY 

This paper deals with text analytics and natural language processing techniques for tracking and summarizing breaking news stories on Twitter. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IR (Information Retrieval), followed by cs.CL (Computation and Language) which deals with natural language processing. The paper also involves social media analysis, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing). Finally, the paper involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society).
